{"tid":2139813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<來了> 特區政府：強烈反對停止引渡  法國要向法治和國際交代","createTime":"2020-08-04T13:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T14:50:04.000Z","uid":227801,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cd81f91829c6f041caa67ee950f6d0b3f496a2a8","tid":2139813,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541839-20200804.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541839-20200804.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=52afe087\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541839-20200804.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cf14c9ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541839-20200804.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n特區政府強烈反對法國停止批准與香港的移交逃犯協定<br />\n2020-08-04 HKT 21:48<br />\n特區政府表示，強烈反對法國停止批准與香港的移交逃犯協定。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，每個國家都有維護國家安全和主權的法例，亦是有職責所在。認為法國政府為了政治目的，以制定港區國安法為借口，宣布停止批准與香港的移交逃犯協定，是粗暴干涉中國內政，特區政府對此強烈反對。又表示法國政府甘心停止批准與香港已簽訂移交逃犯協定，讓犯罪分子繼續有機會逃避法律制裁，法國要就此向法治和國際交代。"},{"pid":"63f8f75e7771cf18be47ec5ef4da195160a48050","tid":2139813,"uid":242831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"公然干預法國內部事務？"},{"pid":"229bae4164d200dffe9f237a2ec568f22f80da9f","tid":2139813,"uid":231583,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2387ab40f41c4d48fa033f36dbf2974f13d76831","tid":2139813,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ea51c1f61319daf557f9fbad2775123cab7c6a5","tid":2139813,"uid":77547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:00:41.000Z","msg":"我法國啲新聞日日一樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":